<div class="glossary-box"><span class="gls-title">// Glossary</span>
<strong>TAM</strong> — Total Addressable Market: total global opportunity<br>
<strong>SAM</strong> — Serviceable Addressable Market: portion you can serve<br>
<strong>SOM</strong> — Serviceable Obtainable Market: portion you can realistically capture<br>
<strong>Primary research</strong> — Original data you collect yourself
