on(this,9,2,1,1)">Timeline over which equity ownership is earned</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,2,2,1)">A salary schedule</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,2,3,1)">A product release plan</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-9-2"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-9-3"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q4</span>What is a cliff in equity vesting?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,3,0,1)">A dramatic business decision</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,3,1,1)">The period before any equity vests (typically 1 year)</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,3,2,1)">A funding round deadline</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,3,3,1)">A type of investor</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-9-3"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-9-4"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q5</span>Why can equal 50/50 equity splits be problematic?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,4,0,1)">One founder always works harder</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,4,1,1)">They can cause deadlock on decisions with no tiebreaker</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,4,2,1)">They are illegal</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,4,3,1)">Investors do not allow them</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-9-4"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-9-5"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q6</span>How much equity is typically reserved as employee option pool?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,5,0,1)">1-2%</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,5,1,1)">10-15%</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,5,2,1)">50%</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,9,5,3,1)">None</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-9-5"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="