<strong>Burn rate</strong> — Monthly cash expenditure<br>
<strong>Runway</strong> — Months of operation remaining at current burn rate<br>
<strong>CAC</strong> — Customer Acquisition Cost<br>
<strong>LTV</strong> — Lifetime Value: total revenue from one customer<br>
<strong>Gross margin</strong> — Revenue minus COGS as percentage of revenue
