v></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-19-9"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q10</span>What is the first step to improving retention?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,19,9,0,1)">Spend more on marketing</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,19,9,1,1)">Measure it — know your churn rate and where customers drop off</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,19,9,2,1)">Hire more customer service staff</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,19,9,3,1)">Improve your packaging</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-19-9"></div></div></div><div class="quiz-actions"><span class="quiz-answered-count" id="qcount-19"><span>0</span>/10 answered</span><button class="quiz-submit-btn" id="qsub-19" onclick="submitQuiz(19)" disabled>Submit Test &#8594;</button></div><div class="quiz-result" id="qres-19" style="display:none"></div></div></div>
