ption" onclick="selectOption(this,25,2,1,1)">Making misleading claims about environmental responsibility to appear more sustainable than you are</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,2,2,1)">A recycling programme</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,2,3,1)">A marketing colour trend</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-25-2"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-25-3"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q4</span>Why does ethical business matter beyond moral reasons?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,3,0,1)">It does not — only profits matter</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,3,1,1)">Ethical businesses attract better talent, build stronger loyalty, access impact capital, and avoid regulatory crises</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,3,2,1)">Ethics has no business impact</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,3,3,1)">Only large companies benefit</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-25-3"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-25-4"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q5</span>What is impact investing?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,4,0,1)">Investing for highest financial return only</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,4,1,1)">Investment seeking positive social or environmental outcomes alongside financial returns</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,4,2,1)">Charitable donations</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,4,3,1)">Government spending</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-25-4"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-25-5"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q6</span>What is supply chain ethics?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,5,0,1)">Speed and cost efficiency of your supply chain</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,25,5,1