tOption(this,26,2,2,2)">42%</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,2,3,2)">80%</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-26-2"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-26-3"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q4</span>What is a post-mortem in startup context?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,3,0,1)">A hospital procedure</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,3,1,1)">A structured analysis of what went wrong to extract actionable lessons</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,3,2,1)">A late-night work session</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,3,3,1)">A product shutdown process</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-26-3"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-26-4"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q5</span>What does fail fast mean?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,4,0,1)">Give up quickly at the first challenge</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,4,1,1)">Design small cheap experiments to learn fast and pivot before major investment is wasted</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,4,2,1)">Launch poorly and fix it later</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,4,3,1)">Ignore quality in early stages</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-26-4"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-26-5"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q6</span>What is antifragility?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,5,0,1)">Being resistant to stress</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,5,1,1)">Becoming stronger as a result of stresses and shocks</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,5,2,1)">Being flexible and adaptable</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,26,5,3,1)">Avoiding all risk</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-26-5"></div></div><div class="quiz-q"