<h3>A Final Word</h3>
<p>Africa's greatest challenges need Africa's most determined entrepreneurs. Every tool in this course is now yours. The continent is not waiting for a perfect founder — it is waiting for a committed one. Start imperfectly. Start now. Start today.</p>
