" onclick="selectOption(this,30,5,2,1)">They invest in your business</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,5,3,1)">They provide technical skills</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-30-5"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-30-6"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q7</span>What should your weekly review ritual include?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,6,0,1)">Only celebrating wins</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,6,1,1)">Reviewing what you planned vs what happened, extracting lessons, adjusting the next week accordingly</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,6,2,1)">Only tracking revenue numbers</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,6,3,1)">Team entertainment and motivation</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-30-6"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-30-7"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q8</span>What is the most common reason people do not execute their plan?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,7,0,1)">Lack of talent</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,7,1,1)">Lack of clarity on the next single specific action — big goals paralyse; small concrete steps move</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,7,2,1)">Lack of ideas</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,7,3,1)">Government interference</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-30-7"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-30-8"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q9</span>What is the most important quality for a successful 90-day plan?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,8,0,2)">Genius</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,8,1,2)">A large budget</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,8,2,2)">Consistent imperfect daily action — showing up every day even when you do not feel like it</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,8,3,2)">A perfect plan from the start</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-30-8"></div></div><div class="quiz-q" id="q-30-9"><div class="q-text"><span class="q-num">Q10</span>What is the core message of the final lesson?</div><div class="q-options"><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,9,0,1)">Wait until you are fully ready before starting</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,9,1,1)">Africa needs committed entrepreneurs who start imperfectly now rather than waiting for perfect conditions</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,9,2,1)">Entrepreneurship requires perfect conditions</div><div class="q-option" onclick="selectOption(this,30,9,3,1)">Only funded founders should build</div></div><div class="q-feedback" id="qf-30-9"></div></div></div><div class="quiz-actions"><span class="quiz-answered-count" id="qcount-30"><span>0</span>/10 answered</span><button class="quiz-submit-btn" id="qsub-30" onclick="submitQuiz(30)" disabled>Submit Test &#8594;</button></div><div class="quiz-result" id="qres-30" style="display:none"></div></div></div></div>

</div><!-- end .lessons -->

